      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in style! This vehicle is in good condition and has been well cared for, offering a dependable and smooth ride. The interior is clean and comfortable, making it a fantastic choice for anyone looking for a reliable daily driver that still looks great.",
