    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is. It currently requires significant mechanical attention, as the engine runs roughly and the transmission is slipping. The exterior shows heavy wear with noticeable rust spots and several dents, while the interior has multiple tears in the upholstery and some non-functional electronics. This would make a suitable project car for an enthusiast or a source for parts.",
